s/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對我嚟講大師唔一定要&ldquo;範範掂&rdquo;，而我心目中前無古人後無來者既大師係布烈遜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢所提倡既&ldquo;電影書寫&rdquo;除咗佢之外，完全無人可以做到佢咁極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以睇下佢本書《電影書寫札記》(Notes on Cinematography)，睇完之後包你對電影有另一番睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffebd50d90e076c0a3ad67eeb480c4da569daffe","tid":257262,"uid":1773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Quentin Tarantino<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npulp fiction係佢最好睇嘅作品</blockquote><br />\n劇本寫得最好，其實inglorious bastards同Django都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n影響力係大一定係pulp fiction<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢最成熟既作品既應該係inglourious basterds"},{"pid":"45ca0224f020f5074ee21eace0c93e5d651abb13","tid":257262,"uid":118946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Quentin Tarantino<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npulp fiction係佢最好睇嘅作品</blockquote><br />\n劇本寫得最好，其實inglorious bastards同Django都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n影響力係大一定係pulp fiction<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢最成熟既作品既應該係inglourious basterds</blockquote><br />\n好鍾意佢用flashback介紹d角色<br />\n個奸佬hans landa我認為同Dark Knight Joker一樣並列電影十大惡人之首"},{"pid":"d2dfe2844ebd28c85782aafc02e8354743da61a8","tid":257262,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Christopher Nolan</blockquote><br />\n我覺得佢interstellar係最神</blockquote><br />\n佢套momento<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c28cdadba