le同hugh既演技、極度巧秒既布局同伏線、戲想帶出既msg<br />\n<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7月份上dunkirk 除定褲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw我覺得nolan作品既偉大有賴hans zimmer呢個不世鬼才既配樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢兩個真係絕配，好似speilberg同john williams，王家衛鐵三角呢啲組合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充：nolan細佬johnathon nolan既功勞都極大 好多劇本係佢地兄弟一齊編<br />\n而johnathon同佢老婆create既westworld<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌那星 配埋anthony hopkins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕對係神作！<br />\ndoesn't look like anything to me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74df8fa13d718f819ea8a0c7f4926746fa46538","tid":257262,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:23:45.000Z","msg":"只有jc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n路蘭拍套好睇既愛情片先好講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c9f028942c5822093b0445e416422e3964898a","tid":257262,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Christopher Nolan</blockquote><br />\n一向覺得佢既戲係劇本大過導演<br />\n佢寫劇本係好叻，意念好，但對鏡頭無乜sense<br />\n於我而言，佢係個好編劇但唔係個好導演<br />\n更加稱唔上前無古人 後來無者</b