\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢導嘅都....</blockquote><br />\n只同意屎忽保，列生同占士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9bdeec8ac3314c99863acf26f0696380fd4bff","tid":257262,"uid":57007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過份吹奏Nolan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論商業片前面都仲有Spielberg、James Cameron、George Lucas、Ridley Scott<br />\nNolan咁既資歷點同呢班老野比，攞左獎先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChristoph Nolan 係咪過譽就見人見智啦<br />\n但佢網上真係好多fans<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋 christoph nolan 真係算後生就紅<br />\n呢廿年內出名既荷里活導演無幾多係真係後生過佢而又有咁多fans 追棒 <br />\n<br />\n荷里活九十年代尾，二千年頭初上位果班大部份都老過佢<br />\n<br />\nDavid Fincher, Wes Anderson , QT ,<br />\nSteven Soderbergh , <br />\nBrad Bird ，JJ Abrams , Peter Jackson  ,Richard Linklater<br />\n<br />\n連呢幾年越拍越有既Denis Villeneuve 都老過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我應該會揀高安兄弟<br />\n雖然唔係咩類型都有拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f24478b80ed3ae4efbe35c8c73e7d0d27159e1","tid":257262,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"Quentin Tarantino<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ce15eeb239f6635cb2489299914a4cf9e1bb29","tid":257262,"uid":11185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過份吹奏Nolan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論商業片前面都仲有Spielberg、James Cameron、George Lucas、Ridley Scott<br />\nNolan咁既資歷點同呢班老野比，攞左獎先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLucas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢導嘅都....</blockquote><br />\n只同意屎忽保，列生同占士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLucas係一個生意佬多過導演，佢將一個電影系列賣到出神入化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20db1cc47850618ec3c56dd8e89d856840494b3","tid":257262,"uid":18679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"Kubrick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa9cbc74168d0805f54f72f51e42d9460365bbe","tid":257262,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過份吹奏Nolan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論商業片前面都仲有Spielberg、James Cameron、George Lucas、Ridley Scott<br />\nNolan咁既資歷點同呢班老野比，攞左獎先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撚玩啦伍寶<br />\nGeorge Lucas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係創造左星戰出黎但佢從來都唔係一個好導演啦<br />\n盲奶老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17efab2d09b6c56a35cb7f861521b89f8b312a74","tid":257262,"uid":41309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Christopher Nolan</blockquote><br />\n一向覺得佢既戲係劇本大過導演<br />\n佢寫劇本係好叻，意念好，但對鏡頭無乜sense<br />\n於我而言，佢係個好編劇但唔係個好導演<br />\n更加稱唔上前無古人 後來無者</blockquote><br />\n補充下我既諗法，係佢鏡頭底下始終缺乏人味"},{"pid":"0cf6f2cd24bddbbf33508498ee75810397f3441c","tid":257262,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"個人覺得Nolan 同 Kubrick唔係同一個level <br />\nKubrick 既戲實在太超前 6，70年代拍既（Dr Strangelove, 2001) 依家睇翻完全唔覺老套 <br />\n反而覺得現代導演無一個可以拍到類似Kubrick既戲<br />\n<br />\n不過Nolan 係商業上係超級成功 呢點Kubrick就俾唔上<br />\n唔知邊個話Nolan成功係<br />\n將藝術片商業化 + 震撼cinematic experience<br />\n<br />\n即係如果將故事深度同 cinematic experience 當成兩個極端咁睇<br />\n<br />\nCoen brothers 就係故事深度既一端 (Fargo, Big Lebowski, No Country for old man)<br />\n<br />\n伊拉力圖就係 cinematic experience 既一端 (Birdman, Revenant)<br />\n<br />\nNolan 就係平衡兩邊 不過就係咁就一個Best Director 獎都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然商業上/IMDB 上係顯然超班<br />\n<br />\n利申：Nolan fans"},{"pid":"20fb8507effc08bb2fe22ca84ebb123ed43ef5da","tid":257262,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過份吹奏Nolan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論商業片前面都仲有Spielberg、James Cameron、George Lucas、Ridley Scott<br />\nNolan咁既資歷點同呢班老野比，攞左獎先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撚玩啦伍寶<br />\nGeorge Lucas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係創造左星戰出黎但佢從來都唔係一個好導演啦<br />\n盲奶老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係淨係睇導演功力，點樣無限食老本都係一種功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa63a43cdd1a5a491281203e412712cfc93cd0b","tid":257262,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過份吹奏Nolan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論商業片前面都仲有Spielberg、James Cameron、George Lucas、Ridley Scott<br />\nNolan咁既資歷點同呢班老野比，攞左獎先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撚玩啦伍寶<br />\nGeorge Lucas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係創造左星戰出黎但佢從來都唔係一個好導演啦<br />\n盲奶老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係淨係睇導演功力，點樣無限食老本都係一種功力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nStar Wars好睇嘅集數<br />\n都唔係Lucas本人導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係無可否認 佢係一個好厲害嘅生意人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959c74d4cb747f89f71429baf71f1aef88b61f36","tid":257262,"uid":78390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:11:02.000Z","msg":"Stanley Kubrick確是神<br />\n咩題材都得<br />\n愛情（Eyes Wide Shut)<br />\n科幻 （2001 Space Odyssey)<br />\n戰爭（Full Metal Jacket)<br />\n恐佈（Shining)<br />\n歷史（Barry Lyndon)<br />\n人性（Clockwork Orange)<br />\n簡直掂咩都變經典<br />\n真係天才同神經病一線之差"},{"pid":"08f896a312e198c402c092553f67ad0681701d21","tid":257262,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:24:34.000Z","msg":"塔可夫斯基"},{"pid":"93f40b218d16f03d8a3c532e0526cacd8d97520e","tid":257262,"uid":7339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扣比力克</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n